# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Privacy boundary: personal memory & generated outputs are PRIVATE.
# Never commit or push them to a public remote.
# The shareable artifact is the card/ (logic + default templates) only.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Generated CVs, SOPs, PI reports, per-application folders — contain personal data
/output/*
!/output/.gitkeep
!/output/README.md

# All memory contents are private...
memory/**

# ...but keep the folder skeleton + docs so the STRUCTURE stays shareable
# (data files like profile.md, _manager.md, experience/*.md, uploads/* remain ignored)
!memory/**/
!memory/**/README.md
!memory/**/.gitkeep

# LaTeX build artifacts
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex.gz

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
